The code has 2 source files for DLL functions implementation
  dll.c and dll_cleanup.c
Common header is dll.h

The above DLL implementtaion has to be used by an applcation (app.c) to store a dummy employee information

In this case compilation is done by creating dynamic library:

To run the code :
$ sh create_dynamic_lib.sh
$ sh exec_using_dyn_lib.sh
$ ./run_d.exe 
